%% DG-402: CRUD Islem Sequence Diyagrami
%% Durum: DRAFT
%% Editor: https://mermaid.live
%% Aciklama: Standart CRUD endpoint akisi (herhangi bir resource icin)
%% ---

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Client as Frontend
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant API as API Server
    participant Cache as Redis
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Audit as Audit Log

    Note over User, Audit: === LIST (GET /resources) ===

    User->>Client: Sayfa ac
    Client->>GW: GET /api/v1/resources?page=1&limit=20
    GW->>GW: Rate limit check
    GW->>API: Forward + Auth header
    API->>API: JWT validate
    API->>Cache: Cache hit?
    alt Cache HIT
        Cache-->>API: Cached data
    else Cache MISS
        API->>DB: SELECT * ... LIMIT 20 OFFSET 0
        DB-->>API: Rows + count
        API->>Cache: SET cache (TTL 5dk)
    end
    API-->>Client: 200 {data: [...], meta: {page, total}}

    Note over User, Audit: === CREATE (POST /resources) ===

    User->>Client: Form doldur + gonder
    Client->>GW: POST /api/v1/resources {body}
    GW->>API: Forward
    API->>API: JWT validate + RBAC check
    API->>API: Input validation (schema)
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO resources
    DB-->>API: New record
    API->>Cache: Invalidate list cache
    API->>Audit: INSERT audit_log (action: INSERT)
    API-->>Client: 201 {data: newRecord}

    Note over User, Audit: === UPDATE (PUT /resources/:id) ===

    User->>Client: Duzenle + kaydet
    Client->>GW: PUT /api/v1/resources/123 {body}
    GW->>API: Forward
    API->>API: JWT + RBAC + ownership check
    API->>API: Input validation
    API->>DB: UPDATE resources SET ... WHERE id=123
    DB-->>API: Updated record
    API->>Cache: Invalidate (item + list)
    API->>Audit: INSERT audit_log (action: UPDATE, old_values, new_values)
    API-->>Client: 200 {data: updatedRecord}

    Note over User, Audit: === DELETE (DELETE /resources/:id) ===

    User->>Client: Sil butonuna tikla + onayla
    Client->>GW: DELETE /api/v1/resources/123
    GW->>API: Forward
    API->>API: JWT + RBAC check
    API->>DB: UPDATE resources SET deleted_at=NOW() (soft delete)
    DB-->>API: OK
    API->>Cache: Invalidate
    API->>Audit: INSERT audit_log (action: DELETE)
    API-->>Client: 204 No Content
